data.config:
[Global]
secret-name = openstack-credentials
secret-namespace = kube-system
region = regionOne
[LoadBalancer]
use-octavia = True

data.install-config:
apiVersion: v1
baseDomain: zerotodevops.com
compute:
- architecture: amd64
  hyperthreading: Enabled
  name: worker
  platform: {}
  replicas: 0
controlPlane:
  architecture: amd64
  hyperthreading: Enabled
  name: master
  platform: {}
  replicas: 3
metadata:
  creationTimestamp: null
  name: ocpinternallb
networking:
  clusterNetwork:
  - cidr: 10.128.0.0/14
    hostPrefix: 23
  machineNetwork:
  - cidr: 10.0.0.0/16
  networkType: OpenShiftSDN
  serviceNetwork:
  - 172.30.0.0/16
platform:
  openstack:
    apiFloatingIP: 192.168.5.145
    apiVIP: 10.0.0.5
    cloud: standalone
    defaultMachinePlatform:
      type: m1.2xlarge
    externalDNS: null
    externalNetwork: public
    ingressVIP: 10.0.0.7
publish: External
pullSecret: ""
sshKey: |
  ssh-rsa  stack@osp.home.lab
